@{
  ViewData["Title"] = "Legal Disclosures";
  ViewData["IsHeroPage"] = false;
}

<main class="flex-grow pt-28 pb-20 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-[1440px] mx-auto w-full text-left">

  <header class="mb-12 flex flex-col items-start">
    <div class="w-2 h-10 bg-acid-mint mb-6"></div>
    <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tighter break-words w-full">
      LEGAL DISCLOSURES
    </h1>
    <p class="font-body text-sm font-light text-on-surface-variant mt-4 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
      Last updated: May 2026. These disclosures govern your active interaction with CARVIA digital properties, technical registries, and performance curated logs. Read carefully.
    </p>
  </header>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 border-t border-outline-variant/30 pt-8">

    <aside class="hidden lg:block lg:col-span-3">
      <div class="sticky top-28 flex flex-col space-y-4">
        <p class="font-mono text-[10px] font-bold text-on-surface-variant opacity-50 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Index</p>
        <a class="font-mono text-[11px] font-bold text-acid-mint hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity tracking-widest" href="#terms">01. TERMS OF SERVICE</a>
        <a class="font-mono text-[11px] font-bold text-white hover:text-acid-mint transition-colors tracking-widest" href="#privacy">02. PRIVACY POLICY</a>
        <a class="font-mono text-[11px] font-bold text-white hover:text-acid-mint transition-colors tracking-widest" href="#cookies">03. COOKIE DIRECTIVE</a>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <div class="lg:col-span-9 flex flex-col space-y-16">

      <section class="scroll-mt-28" id="terms">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-6 flex items-center tracking-tight">
          <span class="text-acid-mint mr-3 font-mono text-lg">01 //</span> Terms of Service
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 font-body text-sm font-light text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Welcome to CARVIA. By accessing our platform, configuring a vehicle, or interacting with our digital registry architecture, you are entering into a binding agreement structured around absolute clarity and uncompromising standards. The services provided are subject to the notices, terms, and conditions set forth herein.
          </p>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to modify these terms. Continued utilization of our digital surfaces following any adjustments indicates your mandatory acceptance of the revised protocol. Our vehicles are precision instruments; our terms reflect the same meticulous rigor.
          </p>
          <ul class="border-l border-outline-variant pl-6 space-y-3 my-6 font-mono text-[11px] tracking-wider uppercase">
            <li><strong class="text-white normal-case">1.1 User Obligations:</strong> You agree to provide accurate telemetry when requested and not to reverse-engineer our configuration interfaces.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white normal-case">1.2 Intellectual Property:</strong> The brutalist aesthetics, proprietary typography, and vehicle schematics remain the sole property of CARVIA.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white normal-case">1.3 Limitation of Liability:</strong> CARVIA is not legally liable for increased heart rates or adrenaline spikes resulting from viewing model specifications.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="w-full h-px bg-outline-variant/20"></div>

      <section class="scroll-mt-28" id="privacy">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-6 flex items-center tracking-tight">
          <span class="text-acid-mint mr-3 font-mono text-lg">02 //</span> Privacy Policy
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 font-body text-sm font-light text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Your data is handled with the same security protocols as our automated backend architectures. We collect telemetry strictly to enhance your tracking configuration experience across your private curator dashboards.
          </p>
          <p>
            We do not sell your personal identifiers to third-party data brokers. The data architecture is designed as a closed loop, ensuring that your interactions inside the car specs update cycles remain entirely confidential.
          </p>
          <p>
            For a complete data extraction request, contact our security annex configuration pathways directly at <a class="text-acid-mint hover:underline underline-offset-4 font-mono" href="mailto:privacy@carvia.io">privacy@carvia.io</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="w-full h-px bg-outline-variant/20"></div>

      <section class="scroll-mt-28" id="cookies">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-6 flex items-center tracking-tight">
          <span class="text-acid-mint mr-3 font-mono text-lg">03 //</span> Cookie Directive
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 font-body text-sm font-light text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            This terminal uses tracking nodes (cookies) to maintain identity session integrity, analyze layout interactions across our high-contrast interfaces, and store your uploaded visual staging configurations securely.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-6">
            <div class="border border-outline-variant/50 p-5 rounded-[2px] bg-surface-container hover:border-acid-mint transition-colors group">
              <h3 class="font-mono text-xs text-white mb-1 uppercase group-hover:text-acid-mint transition-colors">Essential Nodes</h3>
              <p class="font-body text-xs font-light text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Required for the terminal to function safely. Cannot be disabled without terminating active encrypted browser loops.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border border-outline-variant/50 p-5 rounded-[2px] bg-surface-container hover:border-acid-mint transition-colors group">
              <h3 class="font-mono text-xs text-white mb-1 uppercase group-hover:text-acid-mint transition-colors">Telemetry Nodes</h3>
              <p class="font-body text-xs font-light text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Aggregates layout interaction data to refine the overall editorial and loading flow of our performance showcases.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</main>